# DnD Companion — Backend WebSocket

Real-time kapsam **dar**: yalnızca DM Screen live fields (HP, temp HP, conditions, death saves) + campaign member join/leave bildirimleri. Dice, initiative, combat tracker MVP dışı.

Transport: Socket.io via `@nestjs/websockets`. Contract → `docs/03_API_CONTRACTS.md` Bölüm 14; güvenlik → `docs/07` Bölüm 6.

## Modül Yapısı

```
websocket/
  websocket.module.ts    # Redis adapter init
  websocket.gateway.ts   # Connection, rooms, broadcast helpers
  websocket.guard.ts     # Opsiyonel message-level guard
```

Gateway export edilir; `CharactersService` live PATCH sonrası `broadcastLiveUpdate` çağırır.

## Handshake Authentication [AUTH-004]

Client access token'ı `auth` objesinde gönderir:

```typescript
// Client (referans)
io(url, { auth: { token: accessToken } });
```

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — handleConnection
async handleConnection(client: Socket) {
  try {
    const token = client.handshake.auth?.token;
    if (!token) throw new Error('No token');

    const payload = this.jwtService.verify(token, { secret: process.env.JWT_ACCESS_SECRET });
    const user = await this.prisma.user.findUnique({
      where: { id: payload.sub },
      select: { id: true, username: true, role: true, isActive: true },
    });
    if (!user || !user.isActive) throw new Error('Invalid user');

    client.data.userId = user.id;
    client.data.username = user.username;
    client.data.role = user.role;
  } catch {
    client.disconnect(true);
  }
}

// ✗ Yanlış — token doğrulamadan room join'e izin
async handleConnection(client: Socket) {
  client.data.userId = client.handshake.query.userId;
}
```

Token yok/geçersiz → anında disconnect. HTTP `401` yok — WS pattern.

## Room Modeli

Room adı: `campaign:<campaignId>` (kebab-case event adları, room prefix colon).

Client otomatik tüm room'lara girmez — explicit `join-campaign`.

## Room Join Authorization

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — join-campaign handler
@SubscribeMessage('join-campaign')
async handleJoinCampaign(client: Socket, payload: { campaignId: string }) {
  const userId = client.data.userId;
  if (!userId) return;

  const campaign = await this.prisma.campaign.findUnique({
    where: { id: payload.campaignId },
    include: { members: { select: { userId: true } } },
  });

  if (!campaign) {
    client.emit('error', {
      event: 'join-campaign',
      message: 'Campaign not found',
      code: 'NOT_FOUND',
    });
    return;
  }

  const isMember =
    campaign.ownerId === userId ||
    campaign.members.some((m) => m.userId === userId) ||
    client.data.role === Role.ADMIN;

  if (!isMember) {
    client.emit('error', {
      event: 'join-campaign',
      message: 'Not a member of this campaign',
      code: 'FORBIDDEN',
    });
    return;
  }

  client.join(`campaign:${payload.campaignId}`);
  client.emit('joined-campaign', { campaignId: payload.campaignId });
}

// ✗ Yanlış — üyelik kontrolü olmadan join
client.join(`campaign:${payload.campaignId}`);
```

DM = `ownerId`; `campaign_members` DM içermez — owner check zorunlu.

## Event İsimlendirme

Client → Server (kebab-case):

| Event | Payload |
| --- | --- |
| `join-campaign` | `{ campaignId: string }` |
| `leave-campaign` | `{ campaignId: string }` |

Server → Client (room broadcast):

| Event | Açıklama |
| --- | --- |
| `character:live-update` | Live field değişimi |
| `campaign:member-joined` | Yeni üye |
| `campaign:member-left` | Üye ayrıldı |

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — colon namespace server event
this.server.to(`campaign:${campaignId}`).emit('character:live-update', payload);

// ✗ Yanlış — camelCase event
this.server.emit('characterLiveUpdate', payload);
```

## character:live-update Payload

Tek alan veya toplu `fields` objesi — spec ikisini de kabul eder; tercih toplu (daha az event).

```typescript
// Tercih edilen toplu format
{
  characterId: string;
  characterName: string;
  fields: {
    hitPointsCurrent?: number;
    temporaryHitPoints?: number;
    conditions?: string[];
    deathSaves?: { successes: number; failures: number };
  };
  updatedBy: string; // username
}
```

Live update REST kaynağı: `PATCH /characters/:id/live` — persist DB + gateway broadcast. WS tek başına source of truth değil.

## leave-campaign ve Disconnect

```typescript
@SubscribeMessage('leave-campaign')
handleLeaveCampaign(client: Socket, payload: { campaignId: string }) {
  client.leave(`campaign:${payload.campaignId}`);
}
```

`handleDisconnect`: Socket.io otomatik room cleanup — ek iş gerekmez.

## Broadcast Helper'ları (Service API)

Gateway method'ları DI ile service'lere açılır:

```typescript
broadcastLiveUpdate(campaignId: string, data: LiveUpdatePayload): void {
  this.server.to(`campaign:${campaignId}`).emit('character:live-update', data);
}

broadcastMemberJoined(campaignId: string, data: MemberPayload): void {
  this.server.to(`campaign:${campaignId}`).emit('campaign:member-joined', data);
}
```

Invite join service → `broadcastMemberJoined` after member insert.

## Token Expiry [SEC-004]

Access token 15 dk. Client:
1. Refresh HTTP → yeni token
2. WS disconnect + reconnect yeni token ile

Opsiyonel: `reauthenticate` event (spec'te alternatif) — gateway token yeniden verify eder.

Gateway per-message JWT re-verify **yok** (performans); reconnect sorumluluğu client'ta.

## Redis Adapter (Horizontal Scale)

Çok instance WS için `@socket.io/redis-adapter`:

```typescript
// websocket.module.ts / gateway afterInit
async afterInit(server: Server) {
  const pubClient = createClient({ url: process.env.REDIS_URL });
  const subClient = pubClient.duplicate();
  await Promise.all([pubClient.connect(), subClient.connect()]);
  server.adapter(createAdapter(pubClient, subClient));
}
```

Broadcast `server.to(room)` tüm instance'lara yayılır. Redis yoksa single-instance lokal dev yeterli.

## CORS

Gateway CORS: `origin: process.env.FRONTEND_URL`, `credentials: true` — HTTP ile uyumlu.

## Hata Handling (WS)

HTTP exception filter WS'ye uygulanmaz. Hata → client-specific `error` event:

```typescript
client.emit('error', { event: '<source-event>', message: '...', code: 'FORBIDDEN' });
```

Room broadcast hatalarında tüm room'a error yayınlama — yalnızca istek yapan client.

